    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the credibility assessment plan at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision that the centrifugal blood pump design meets the hemolysis performance criterion (RH < 1.0) relative to the predicate device across the full CPB operating envelope.",
